body:
[Skip the "*" if you want your editing ASAP]

Introduction:
Soooooo... I've been quite inactive for this community for the last year and a half just because I'm living life to the max!

I've recently been running out of raw footage to edit. I have seen that the YouTube community on here has grown since I last left it, and I would love to edit your videos.

*Steps:
-  *Try keeping the files lower than 1G* --> The raw video on a compressed.                        
- Inside the compressed file send in what you would like to see in your video. [If you have any intro, song, etc, send it please] [Also send me the email you want me to send you the completed video in, it'll be on .mov format unless you want it on another way].
- Send the file download to cobaltdoesmc@gmail.com [No .rar's].                                                                
- Wait around a day to a week for it to be done [Depends on my schedule and vsplesk's].                                                     
- I'll send it to you to the email you give on the compressed file.

Contact me in Skype!- Skype: c0balt838

Stuff I do:
  • Rekt effects with after effects.
  • Cinematics [Just if you provide RAW images, not videos!]
  • Intros. [As long as you provide me or vsplesk a template]
  • Logo adding.
  • Intro adding with transparency.
  • Green screening transparency.
  • Color Correction. [CC]
  • Music adding and synchronizing the music with the footage.
  • Montages
  • Fade-ons, fade-ins and all those fancy transitions effects.
  • Outros with video redirects.
  • Thumbnails.
